18/01/2011
BERLIN, Germany -- Croatia's Embassy in Berlin received a parcel Monday (January 17th) containing a hand grenade. An accompanying letter threatened Croatian President Ivo Josipovic for efforts to improve ties with Serbian counterpart Boris Tadic. The letter was signed with the initials HF. Josipovic kicks off a three-day visit to Berlin on Wednesday. (HRT, Hina, Nova TV, Vecernji List, Index, AFP - 17/01/11)
